text: A collectable or collectible (American English) is any object regarded as being of value or interest to a collector. Collectables or collectibles may also refer to: * Collectables Records, a record label * Collectables by Ashanti, a 2005 Ashanti album * Collectibles Vol 1, a compilation album by Willie P. Bennett ==See also== * List of collectibles
title: Collectable (disambiguation)
